*   **Red Lion DA50N** All versions of the DA50N networking gateway are impacted by vulnerabilities such as insufficient verification of data authenticity (CVE-2022-26516), weak password requirements (CVE-2022-1039), and insufficiently protected credentials (CVE-2022-27179).
